{"tid":2051689,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【獨家】傳利豐裁減香港採購部七成員工 公司回應：調整員工編制","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:56:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a70924ea9197db0725a6200b3c50eb1007f08aa1","tid":2051689,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"利豐（前上市編號，494）上月在小股東反對聲音下通過私有化後，目前利豐內部更面臨大重組，有利豐員工向本報爆料稱，該公司上周開始通知解散數百人的香港採購部約七成員工，並指上海及深圳亦有裁員，惟未知實際裁員規模，形容「好似想直情唔做咁」，估計集團想將業務外判內地，從而節省成本。利豐回覆本報時未有說明裁員細節，但指疫情衝擊業務而需調整員工編制。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/finance/20200605/BRBOLNRLQWWYBGZTJRMQQYDTYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200605%2FBRBOLNRLQWWYBGZTJRMQQYDTYM%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5ElQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=5c789a7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200605%2FBRBOLNRLQWWYBGZTJRMQQYDTYM%2F&h=1fd1fb8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/finance/20200605/BRBOLNRLQWWYBGZTJRMQQYDTYM/</a>"},{"pid":"aacdf3d2c13d54ad7fbb177483ddd795fc3eff0e","tid":2051689,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:38:54.000Z","msg":"494呢隻由最高$20趺到去最低0.65<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d12e0858d7a9d646e0179184c9c91e2923cf9a0","tid":2051689,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aacdf3d2c13d54ad7fbb177483ddd795fc3eff0e","tid":2051689,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:38:54.000Z","msg":"494呢隻由最高$20趺到去最低0.65<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:49:52.000Z","msg":"咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr